Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.41,0:01:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,THE DARK LORD HADLAR'S RETURN
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.45,0:02:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.53,0:02:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That crafty little...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.91,0:02:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Doragoramu!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.84,0:02:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Master turned into a Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.92,0:02:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Dorogoramu! It's an ancient\Nmythical attack spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.26,0:02:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought I'd see it used!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.56,0:02:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He's much bigger than the last one!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.44,0:02:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Among all monsters,\NDragons are the most powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Only a true Hero can fight one\Nand overcome it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.95,0:03:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Now face me, Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.53,0:03:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This is going too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.62,0:03:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back, Grampa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A Dragon's skin is harder than steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.97,0:03:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll use Avan Style Sword Technique,\NEarth Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot win simply with brute strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.35,0:03:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.08,0:03:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.79,0:03:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?! Don't scare me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.04,0:03:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Listen, I wasn't training\Nto compete with Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.42,0:04:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be perfectly clear about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.59,0:04:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what sort of\Nheavy training he's doing's, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Avan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.31,0:04:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,How could he do something like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.61,0:04:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai can barely use Hyado! How is he\Ngoing to stop a Dragon's flames?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.87,0:04:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.16,0:04:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.25,0:04:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine, Grampa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.96,0:04:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Earth Slash is a strength-based attack.\NI can't face a Dragon's flames with it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.26,0:04:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Slice the earth, slice the sea,\Nslice the air.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The Avan Style Sword Technique\Nis based on these three skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, you attained Earth Slash,\Nthe ability to slice the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.06,0:05:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I shall explain the next skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Slice the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.40,0:05:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The key to this attack is speed.\NIn other words, agility.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.07,0:05:07.99,On Top,,0,0,0,,WAVE SLASH\NSPEED
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Beating a Dragon's flames\Nrequires an attack that slices the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.62,0:05:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wave Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Avan Style Sword Technique...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.84,0:05:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you've caught on.\NBut will it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.14,0:05:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it, Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.19,0:05:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Wave Slash!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.94,0:05:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He sliced... the flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.80,0:06:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.85,0:06:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.27,0:06:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It stings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.86,0:06:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your own fault, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Using Dorogoramu for training is crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What if you burned Dai to a crisp?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, remember when Dai split the sea\Nwhen he faced that Gargoyle?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.91,0:06:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought he might be able\Nto pull off Wave Slash right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do things like that on a hunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem rather upset.\NWere you really that worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.55,0:06:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No I wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.72,0:06:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If Earth Slash is a strength attack,\NWave Slash is a speed attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,With the strength you already had, your\Nspeed has increased these last few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So he was able to slice the flames\Nwith the pressure from his quick slash.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. Wave Slash is for slicing\Nformless things like fire and water.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Precisely!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.66,0:07:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If you master this skill, you can slice\Nflames and blizzards to attack enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.38,0:07:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And Dai has already figured out\Nhow to do Wave Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.88,0:07:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, completing the\NSpecial Hard Course could be a reality...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It stings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe a light Hyado spell to cool it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, perhaps Dai should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.48,0:07:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That might be perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.27,0:07:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Hyado!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.61,0:07:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A very nice size!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.57,0:07:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by "nice"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This is quite embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But Popp, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.05,0:08:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.67,0:08:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I was forced to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.59,0:08:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. Popp was training alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.14,0:08:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.01,0:08:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? To compete with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.64,0:08:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Knock it off! I wasn't training!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.65,0:08:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,An earthquake!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.40,0:08:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? A volcanic eruption?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.74,0:08:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No. It's something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.74,0:08:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This shaking...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,is from someone trying to\Nbreach the island's magic circle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.83,0:08:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A servant of the Dark Lord of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.47,0:09:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This island is protected\Nby a magic circle that repels evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.27,0:09:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Only bad guys can't come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.93,0:09:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But a normal monster\Nwouldn't be able to set foot inside.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.40,0:09:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could it be...?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.20,0:09:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Did they give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.58,0:09:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.58,0:09:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Something really powerful is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I can feel its evil energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.88,0:09:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Grampa, what's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I know this intense energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.38,0:09:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears my fears were correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.82,0:09:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Your magic circle was quite an annoyance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.07,0:10:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're really back, Dark Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.24,0:10:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark Lord?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Dark Lord?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.12,0:10:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadlar!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.33,0:10:12.59,On Top,,0,0,0,,THE RESURRECTED DARK LORD\NHADLAR
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.01,0:10:20.55,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}DORAGORAMU{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}\NFIRE DRAGON TRANSFORMATION SPELL
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.06,0:10:25.56,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}BAGIKUROSAI{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}\NVORTEX-TYPE SPELL
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.14,0:10:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dark Lord Hadlar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.56,0:10:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no mistaking it.\NIt's the Dark Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.49,0:10:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And that face and body...\NHe looks younger than I remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He's overflowing with vitality!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while, Avan, the Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.01,0:10:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hero?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:11:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Master is the Hero?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.26,0:11:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Long ago, you thwarted\Nall of my ambitions,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.72,0:11:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and even took my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will never forget\Nthat pain and humiliation!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You've already taken\Nhundreds of human lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Compared to a Darkling like me,\Nhumans are nothing more than chattel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My life is worth more than thousands,\Nif not hundreds of millions of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.38,0:11:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No. You're even more\Ndisgusting than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've grown tired of your Hero antics.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.47,0:11:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! Avan, the Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The name of the legendary Hero
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.89,0:11:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,who fought and defeated the Dark Lord,\Nand brought peace to the world
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.19,0:11:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,was Avan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true, Master?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:11:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.78,0:12:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Now stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.99,0:12:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I'll fight with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! Come on!\NYou too, gramps!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.71,0:12:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Popp?!\NI have to fight, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You moron!\NWe'll only get in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.43,0:12:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe Master\Nwas the Hero who killed the Dark Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.18,0:12:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I chose the wrong person to learn under!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.19,0:12:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So those are your students.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.02,0:12:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear you're going about as a Hero tutor\Ntraining warriors of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect that you'd return, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.16,0:12:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How futile.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}IORA!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad that you came here yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.39,0:13:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I can defeat you here\Nand clear the darkness clouding the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.22,0:13:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What rubbish!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.15,0:13:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Begirama!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.28,0:13:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.64,0:13:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What farce is this, Avan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.27,0:13:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't work?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.27,0:14:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Heat and explosion-type spells\Nare my forte!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.15,0:14:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you think you could defeat me\Nwith an ember like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.19,0:14:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.11,0:14:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a true Begirama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Begirama!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.62,0:14:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Wave Slash!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.71,0:14:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What power...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.10,0:14:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're even stronger\Nthan when we last fought.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.02,0:14:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to know?\NYou'll regret hearing the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.78,0:14:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you still believe\Nthat I'm the Dark Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.12,0:14:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.78,0:14:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I was resurrected through the power\Nof a mighty ruler!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.12,0:15:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He gave me\Na more powerful body than before!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.71,0:15:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There's someone stronger\Nthan the Dark Lord?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.68,0:15:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Vearn, the Dark King.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.93,0:15:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dark King...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.06,0:15:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Vearn?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right!\NIt was Vearn, the Dark King!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.69,0:15:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A mighty god of the Underworld\Nwho resurrected me after my defeat to you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.74,0:15:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A god of the Underworld?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.24,0:15:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to sleep for over a decade\Nto replenish the power I lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,but after my return,\NI swore loyalty to Lord Vearn,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.91,0:15:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and was granted rule over his entire\NDark Army as his right hand man!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I am now supreme commander\Nover Lord Vearn's armies!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Hadlar, the Dark Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.34,0:15:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.26,0:15:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There's someone stronger than him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.85,0:15:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over! This world is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.43,0:16:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Vearn, the Dark King is my master\Nand an omnipotent Dark God!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.19,0:16:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,His armies are far greater than\Nmine ever were!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.90,0:16:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what you do,\Nyou humans have no hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.07,0:16:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.04,0:16:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Avan, do you remember\Nour battle 15 years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.25,0:16:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I offer you the same choice\NI did back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.84,0:16:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Join me! Do so and I shall grant you\Nhalf of the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.26,0:16:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you sense your defeat,\Nperhaps you'll be more reasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.40,0:16:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.61,0:16:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Still the same answer.\NYou still can't see my mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.53,0:16:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know what mercy is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.24,0:17:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I agree,\Nyou'd eventually take my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.00,0:17:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I doubt you have the authority\Nto offer half of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.63,0:17:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you're just\Na servant of your Dark King.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.26,0:17:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?! A servant?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You dare call me\Na servant of the Dark King?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.85,0:17:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I see I've struck a nerve.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.69,0:17:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So much for sparing you!\NYour students can watch you turn to ash!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.41,0:17:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the strongest\Nexplosion-type spell there is! Ionazun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.46,0:17:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That stance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.51,0:17:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.59,0:17:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Ionazun!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.01,0:18:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Avan Strash!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.73,0:18:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.53,0:18:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A draw?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.00,0:18:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, the attack that took my life,\NAvan Strash.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.00,0:18:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It cuts deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.09,0:18:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,However!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.43,0:18:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears it lacks the edge\Nover my resurrected power!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.40,0:18:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.83,0:19:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.83,0:19:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.04,0:19:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid! How can we\Nfight someone even Master can't beat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.13,0:19:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Master used Dorogoramu in our training!\NHe barely has any Magic Power left!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.01,0:19:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard Dorogoramu takes three or four times\Nthe Magic Power of a normal spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.72,0:19:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.39,0:19:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.02,0:19:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You've grown weak, Avan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.48,0:19:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I suppose this is\Nthe limit of a human's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.36,0:19:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me ease your suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.58,0:19:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.79,0:19:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to die that much,\Nstudent of Avan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.05,0:20:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.81,0:20:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.94,0:20:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn... it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean nothing to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.58,0:20:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to live, get out of my sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.08,0:20:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.08,0:20:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.43,0:20:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.93,0:20:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood?! Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.55,0:20:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That little brat's blade\Ndrew blood from me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.98,0:20:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.15,0:21:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.95,0:21:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I've changed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.16,0:21:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose no student of Avan\Ncan be left alive after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.13,0:21:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll slaughter you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.63,0:21:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp! Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.34,0:21:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Begirama!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.08,0:21:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.11,0:22:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kindness is the magic of kind people{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.11,0:22:25.99,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}yasashisa wa yasashii hito ga tsukaeru mahou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.15,0:22:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then do I have no choice\NBut to just be a normal person?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.15,0:22:32.99,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}jaa boku wa tada no hito de iru shikanaino?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.16,0:22:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not sure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.16,0:22:36.21,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}doudarou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.50,0:22:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if the place I call home may change{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.50,0:22:44.17,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kaeru basho wa ne kawatte yuku kedo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.34,0:22:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Listen to me, Mother{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.34,0:22:46.72,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}naa kaasan boku wa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.88,0:22:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will never change those I protect{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.88,0:22:52.85,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mamoru hito wo kaetari shinai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.31,0:22:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder what you'd say{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.31,0:22:57.52,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}anata wa nannte iukana{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.69,0:23:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At times I can be cowardly and small{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.69,0:23:01.73,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tokiyori yowaki de chippoke de{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.90,0:23:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What would you say to me\NAs I hesitate to even hesitate?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.90,0:23:08.20,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mayou koto ni mo mayou boku ni nannte iukana{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.36,0:23:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unlike the today that I sought{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.36,0:23:14.03,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sagashite ita kyou to chigatte{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.20,0:23:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure you'd laugh at my disappointment{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.20,0:23:19.33,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ochikonnde shimau boku wo warau no darou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.85,0:23:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The resurrected Hadlar's power\Nwas overwhelming.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.18,0:23:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even Avan, who had once defeated him,\Nis forced into a corner.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.44,0:23:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When Avan shows his willingness to die\Nto protect Dai and for peace,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.90,0:23:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}once again Dai's power awakens!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.95,0:23:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next time on{\i0}\NDRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.58,0:23:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The Insignia of Avan"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.50,0:24:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i0}
